generatedPrompts.frontCover: A charming, humorous watercolor illustration of a sophisticated llama wearing a tiny, tilted party hat and stylish eyeglasses. Floating around the llama are a few delicate, pastel-colored soap bubbles, catching the light. The entire scene is rendered in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the colors. The background is a clean, minimalist wash of a single soft color. Flat 2D artwork.
